<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Jonas Brandt – Ernährungsberatung</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,700;0,9..144,900;1,9..144,300;1,9..144,700&family=Figtree:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
:root{
  --ink:   #0E1714;
  --mid:   #2C3B36;
  --rust:  #C94B25;
  --warm:  #E8A87C;
  --taupe: #B8A99A;
  --bg:    #F0EDE6;
  --bg2:   #E8E3DA;
  --paper: #FAFAF5;
}

*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}

body{
  font-family:'Figtree',sans-serif;
  background:var(--bg);
  color:var(--ink);
  overflow-x:hidden;
}

/* ── CURSOR ── */
.cursor{
  width:10px;height:10px;background:var(--rust);border-radius:50%;
  position:fixed;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999;
  transform:translate(-50%,-50%);transition:transform .1s,width .3s,height .3s;
}
.cursor-ring{
  width:36px;height:36px;border:1px solid var(--rust);border-radius:50%;
  position:fixed;pointer-events:none;z-index:9998;
  transform:translate(-50%,-50%);transition:transform .18s ease,width .3s,height .3s,opacity .3s;
  opacity:0.5;
}

/* ── NAV – vertical left sidebar ── */
.sidebar{
  position:fixed;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:72px;
  background:var(--ink);
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  padding:36px 0;
  z-index:200;
}
.sidebar-logo{
  writing-mode:vertical-rl;
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:.95rem;font-weight:700;
  color:var(--bg);letter-spacing:.12em;
  text-transform:uppercase;cursor:default;
  transform:rotate(180deg);
}
.sidebar-links{
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:32px;list-style:none;
}
.sidebar-links a{
  writing-mode:vertical-rl;
  font-size:.62rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--taupe);text-decoration:none;
  transform:rotate(180deg);transition:color .2s;
}
.sidebar-links a:hover{color:var(--warm);}
.sidebar-dot{
  width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--rust);
}

/* ── MAIN CONTENT (offset by sidebar) ── */
.page{margin-left:72px;}

/* ── HERO ── */
.hero{
  min-height:100vh;
  background:var(--bg);
  display:grid;
  grid-template-rows:1fr auto;
  padding:0 80px 64px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}

.hero-top{
  display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:space-between;
  padding-top:80px;
}

.hero-eyebrow{
  font-size:.72rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--taupe);
  opacity:0;animation:rise .8s .2s forwards;
}
.hero-eyebrow span{color:var(--rust);}

.hero-tag-right{
  text-align:right;
  font-size:.72rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--taupe);letter-spacing:.06em;
  line-height:1.8;
  opacity:0;animation:rise .8s .3s forwards;
}

.hero-center{
  padding:40px 0 0;
  position:relative;z-index:2;
}

.hero-title{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:clamp(4.5rem,10vw,11.5rem);
  font-weight:900;
  line-height:.9;
  letter-spacing:-.03em;
  color:var(--ink);
  margin-bottom:0;
}
.hero-title .italic{
  font-style:italic;
  font-weight:300;
  color:var(--rust);
  font-size:clamp(3.5rem,8vw,9rem);
}
.hero-title .outline{
  color:transparent;
  -webkit-text-stroke:1.5px var(--ink);
}

/* Big decorative number */
.hero-deco{
  position:absolute;
  right:-40px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-60%);
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:38vw;font-weight:900;
  color:rgba(14,23,20,.04);
  line-height:1;user-select:none;pointer-events:none;
  letter-spacing:-.05em;
}

.hero-bottom{
  display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:space-between;
  padding-top:60px;
  border-top:1px solid rgba(14,23,20,.12);
}

.hero-sub{
  font-size:1rem;font-weight:300;line-height:1.8;
  color:var(--mid);max-width:380px;
  opacity:0;animation:rise .8s .7s forwards;
}

.hero-cta-group{
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:20px;
  opacity:0;animation:rise .8s .85s forwards;
}
.hero-stats-row{
  display:flex;gap:48px;
}
.hstat-num{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:2.4rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);
  line-height:1;letter-spacing:-.02em;
}
.hstat-num sup{font-size:.5em;vertical-align:super;color:var(--rust);}
.hstat-label{font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--taupe);margin-top:4px;}

.btn-main{
  background:var(--rust);color:var(--paper);
  font-family:'Figtree',sans-serif;font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600;
  letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;
  padding:16px 40px;border-radius:2px;
  text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;
  transition:background .25s,transform .2s;
}
.btn-main:hover{background:#b33f1e;transform:translateY(-2px);}

/* ── MARQUEE BAND ── */
.marquee-band{
  background:var(--rust);
  padding:14px 0;overflow:hidden;white-space:nowrap;
}
.marquee-inner{
  display:inline-flex;gap:0;
  animation:marquee 22s linear infinite;
}
.marquee-item{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:1rem;font-weight:300;font-style:italic;
  color:var(--paper);letter-spacing:.04em;
  padding:0 40px;
}
.marquee-sep{color:rgba(250,250,245,.4);}

/* ── ABOUT ── */
.about{
  background:var(--ink);
  padding:120px 80px;
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 2fr;
  gap:80px;
  align-items:start;
}
.about-label{
  font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--rust);padding-top:8px;
}
.about-right{}
.about-title{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:clamp(2.4rem,4vw,5rem);
  font-weight:700;
  line-height:1.05;
  color:var(--bg);
  letter-spacing:-.02em;
  margin-bottom:40px;
}
.about-title em{font-style:italic;font-weight:300;color:var(--warm);}
.about-body{
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:40px 60px;
}
.about-text{
  font-size:.95rem;font-weight:300;line-height:1.9;
  color:rgba(240,237,230,.65);
  grid-column:span 2;
}
.about-fact{
  border-top:1px solid rgba(240,237,230,.12);
  padding-top:24px;
}
.about-fact-num{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:3rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--warm);
  line-height:1;letter-spacing:-.03em;margin-bottom:8px;
}
.about-fact-label{font-size:.78rem;font-weight:300;color:rgba(240,237,230,.5);line-height:1.6;}

/* ── SERVICES – horizontal rows ── */
.services{
  background:var(--bg);
  padding:0 0 0 0;
}
.services-header{
  padding:100px 80px 56px;
  display:flex;align-items:baseline;justify-content:space-between;
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(14,23,20,.1);
}
.services-title{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:clamp(2rem,3.5vw,3.8rem);
  font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.02em;color:var(--ink);
}
.services-title em{font-style:italic;font-weight:300;color:var(--rust);}
.services-hint{font-size:.72rem;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--taupe);}

.service-row{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:80px 1fr auto;
  align-items:center;
  gap:60px;
  padding:40px 80px;
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(14,23,20,.1);
  cursor:default;
  transition:background .3s;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.service-row::after{
  content:'';
  position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:0;
  background:var(--rust);
  transition:width .4s cubic-bezier(.77,0,.18,1);
}
.service-row:hover::after{width:4px;}
.service-row:hover{background:var(--bg2);}

.srow-num{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:3.5rem;font-weight:900;color:rgba(14,23,20,.08);
  letter-spacing:-.04em;line-height:1;
  transition:color .3s;
}
.service-row:hover .srow-num{color:rgba(201,75,37,.15);}
.srow-center{}
.srow-name{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:clamp(1.4rem,2vw,2.2rem);
  font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--ink);
  margin-bottom:10px;
}
.srow-desc{
  font-size:.85rem;font-weight:300;line-height:1.75;
  color:var(--mid);opacity:.7;max-width:520px;
}
.srow-right{text-align:right;}
.srow-price{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);
  letter-spacing:-.01em;
}
.srow-period{
  font-size:.68rem;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.1em;
  text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--taupe);margin-top:4px;
}
.srow-arrow{
  font-size:1.4rem;color:var(--rust);margin-top:10px;
  opacity:0;transition:opacity .3s,transform .3s;
  transform:translateX(-8px);
}
.service-row:hover .srow-arrow{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0);}

/* ── TESTIMONIAL ── */
.testi{
  background:var(--bg2);
  padding:120px 80px;
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 2fr;
  gap:80px;align-items:center;
}
.testi-left{
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;
}
.testi-label{font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--rust);}
.testi-avatar{
  width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:50%;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--warm),var(--rust));
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:2rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--paper);
}
.testi-name{font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);}
.testi-detail{font-size:.75rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--taupe);}
.testi-stars{color:var(--rust);font-size:1rem;letter-spacing:3px;}

.testi-right{}
.testi-quote-mark{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:8rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--rust);
  line-height:.6;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:.3;
}
.testi-quote{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:clamp(1.5rem,2.5vw,2.6rem);
  font-weight:300;font-style:italic;
  line-height:1.45;color:var(--ink);
  letter-spacing:-.01em;
}
.testi-result{
  margin-top:32px;
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;
  background:var(--rust);color:var(--paper);
  padding:12px 24px;border-radius:2px;
  font-size:.78rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;
}

/* ── PROCESS ── */
.process{
  background:var(--ink);
  padding:120px 80px;
}
.process-head{
  display:flex;align-items:baseline;justify-content:space-between;
  margin-bottom:80px;
}
.process-title{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:clamp(2rem,3.5vw,3.8rem);
  font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.02em;
  color:var(--bg);
}
.process-title em{font-style:italic;font-weight:300;color:var(--warm);}
.process-sub{font-size:.78rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--taupe);max-width:260px;text-align:right;line-height:1.7;}

.steps{display:flex;gap:0;position:relative;}
.steps::before{
  content:'';
  position:absolute;
  top:32px;left:32px;right:32px;height:1px;
  background:rgba(184,169,154,.15);
}
.step{
  flex:1;padding:0 32px;
  position:relative;
}
.step-node{
  width:64px;height:64px;
  border-radius:50%;
  border:1px solid rgba(184,169,154,.3);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  margin-bottom:32px;
  position:relative;z-index:1;
  background:var(--ink);
  transition:border-color .3s,background .3s;
}
.step:hover .step-node{
  border-color:var(--rust);
  background:var(--rust);
}
.step-n{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:900;color:rgba(240,237,230,.3);
  transition:color .3s;
}
.step:hover .step-n{color:var(--paper);}
.step-title{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--bg);
  margin-bottom:12px;
}
.step-desc{
  font-size:.82rem;font-weight:300;line-height:1.75;
  color:rgba(240,237,230,.45);
}

/* ── CTA SECTION ── */
.cta{
  background:var(--bg);
  padding:120px 80px;
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:100px;align-items:center;
}
.cta-left{}
.cta-eyebrow{font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--rust);margin-bottom:20px;}
.cta-title{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:clamp(2.5rem,4.5vw,5.5rem);
  font-weight:900;line-height:.95;letter-spacing:-.03em;
  color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:28px;
}
.cta-title em{font-style:italic;font-weight:300;}
.cta-body{
  font-size:.95rem;font-weight:300;line-height:1.85;
  color:var(--mid);opacity:.8;margin-bottom:48px;max-width:380px;
}
.cta-links{display:flex;gap:32px;align-items:center;}
.link-ghost{
  font-size:.78rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--taupe);text-decoration:none;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
  transition:color .2s,gap .2s;
}
.link-ghost:hover{color:var(--ink);gap:12px;}
.link-ghost::after{content:'→';}

/* form card */
.form-card{
  background:var(--ink);
  border-radius:4px;
  padding:52px 48px;
}
.form-title{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--bg);
  margin-bottom:32px;letter-spacing:-.01em;
}
.form-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--warm);}
.field{margin-bottom:14px;}
.field input,.field select,.field textarea{
  width:100%;
  background:rgba(240,237,230,.06);
  border:1px solid rgba(240,237,230,.12);
  border-radius:2px;
  color:var(--bg);
  font-family:'Figtree',sans-serif;font-size:.88rem;font-weight:300;
  padding:13px 16px;outline:none;
  transition:border-color .2s;
}
.field input::placeholder,.field textarea::placeholder{color:rgba(184,169,154,.5);}
.field input:focus,.field select:focus,.field textarea:focus{border-color:var(--rust);}
.field select{color:rgba(184,169,154,.6);}
.field textarea{height:90px;resize:none;}
.field-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:14px;}
.form-submit{
  width:100%;
  background:var(--rust);color:var(--paper);
  font-family:'Figtree',sans-serif;font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600;
  letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;
  padding:15px;border:none;cursor:pointer;border-radius:2px;
  margin-top:8px;
  transition:background .25s,transform .2s;
}
.form-submit:hover{background:#b33f1e;transform:translateY(-2px);}
.form-note{font-size:.68rem;color:rgba(184,169,154,.4);text-align:center;margin-top:12px;}

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer{
  background:var(--ink);
  border-top:1px solid rgba(240,237,230,.06);
  padding:40px 80px;
  display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
}
.f-logo{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--bg);letter-spacing:-.01em;
}
.f-links{display:flex;gap:28px;list-style:none;}
.f-links a{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--taupe);text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;transition:color .2s;}
.f-links a:hover{color:var(--warm);}
.f-copy{font-size:.7rem;color:rgba(184,169,154,.35);}

/* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
@keyframes rise{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}
@keyframes marquee{0%{transform:translateX(0);}100%{transform:translateX(-50%);}}

.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px);transition:opacity .75s ease,transform .75s ease;}
.reveal.vis{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cursor" id="cur"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="ring"></div>

<!-- SIDEBAR NAV -->
<nav class="sidebar">
  <div class="sidebar-logo">Jonas Brandt</div>
  <ul class="sidebar-links">
    <li><a href="#about">Über mich</a></li>
    <li><a href="#services">Angebote</a></li>
    <li><a href="#process">Ablauf</a></li>
    <li><a href="#cta">Kontakt</a></li>
  </ul>
  <div class="sidebar-dot"></div>
</nav>

<div class="page">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-deco">JB</div>

    <div class="hero-top">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Ernährungsberatung · <span>München</span> · Seit 2015</p>
      <div class="hero-tag-right">
        Diplom-Ökotrophologe<br/>
        Sports Nutritionist ISSN
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-center">
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        <span style="opacity:0;animation:rise .9s .4s forwards;display:block;">BESSER</span>
        <span class="italic" style="opacity:0;animation:rise .9s .55s forwards;display:block;">essen,</span>
        <span class="outline" style="opacity:0;animation:rise .9s .7s forwards;display:block;">MEHR SEIN.</span>
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-bottom">
      <p class="hero-sub">Kein Diätplan von der Stange. Ich entwickle mit dir eine Ernährungsweise, die zu deinem Leben passt – und dort auch bleibt.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta-group">
        <div class="hero-stats-row">
          <div>
            <div class="hstat-num">500<sup>+</sup></div>
            <div class="hstat-label">Klienten</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="hstat-num">10</div>
            <div class="hstat-label">Jahre Erfahrung</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="hstat-num">98<sup>%</sup></div>
            <div class="hstat-label">Weiterempfehlung</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#cta" class="btn-main">Kostenloses Erstgespräch →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MARQUEE -->
  <div class="marquee-band">
    <div class="marquee-inner">
      <span class="marquee-item">Keine Crashdiäten</span><span class="marquee-sep">·</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Nachhaltige Ergebnisse</span><span class="marquee-sep">·</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Individuell & wissenschaftlich</span><span class="marquee-sep">·</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Für Männer, die es ernst meinen</span><span class="marquee-sep">·</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Keine Crashdiäten</span><span class="marquee-sep">·</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Nachhaltige Ergebnisse</span><span class="marquee-sep">·</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Individuell & wissenschaftlich</span><span class="marquee-sep">·</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Für Männer, die es ernst meinen</span><span class="marquee-sep">·</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="about" id="about">
    <div>
      <div class="about-label reveal">Über mich</div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-right">
      <h2 class="about-title reveal">Ich bin Jonas.<br/>Ich hasse <em>sinnlose Verbote.</em></h2>
      <div class="about-body">
        <p class="about-text reveal">Nach meinem Studium der Ökotrophologie und 10 Jahren in der Praxis habe ich eines gelernt: Die meisten Diäten scheitern nicht an Willenskraft, sondern daran, dass sie nicht zur Realität des Menschen passen. Ich baue Ernährungskonzepte, die standhalten – im Alltag, im Stress, im Urlaub.</p>
        <div class="about-fact reveal">
          <div class="about-fact-num">–15 kg</div>
          <div class="about-fact-label">Mein eigener Weg. Ich kenne den Frust aus erster Hand.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-fact reveal">
          <div class="about-fact-num">∅ 11 W</div>
          <div class="about-fact-label">Bis meine Klienten signifikante, nachhaltige Ergebnisse sehen.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-fact reveal">
          <div class="about-fact-num">0</div>
          <div class="about-fact-label">Verbotene Lebensmittel in meinen Konzepten. Null.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section class="services" id="services">
    <div class="services-header reveal">
      <h2 class="services-title">Was ich <em>anbiete</em></h2>
      <span class="services-hint">3 Pakete · Hover für Details</span>
